# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:46
translate spanish hwb_s16a_e99e0c10:

    # Amber "Wanna just heat up our leftovers?"
    Amber "Тебе разогреть то, что осталось?"

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:50
translate spanish hwb_s16a_ba4b9eb1:

    # Marina "Hm…"
    Marina "Хм…"

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:54
translate spanish hwb_s16a_f1bfa58f:

    # Amber "Guessing that’s a no?"
    Amber "Я так понимаю, это значит “нет”?"

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:58
translate spanish hwb_s16a_f87aa85b:

    # Marina "I’m not ready for pancakes again yet. I need a day. Or maybe a week."
    Marina "Я все еще не готова к блинам. Мне нужен день. Или неделя."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:62
translate spanish hwb_s16a_36c09dc5:

    # Amber "Lemme know if you see somewhere you want me to stop."
    Amber "Дай знать, если захочешь где-нибудь остановиться."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:64
translate spanish hwb_s16a_89208912:

    # "Now that it’s approaching evening, there aren’t any more massive traffic jams going through Moab. We can cruise through at a steady pace, just like when we first got into Arches."
    "Ahora que se acerca la tarde, ya no hay tantos embotellamientos enormes al pasar por Moab. Podemos avanzar a un ritmo constante, igual que cuando llegamos a Arches."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:70
translate spanish hwb_s16a_65e75fc3:

    # "Until I slam on the brakes." with vpunch
    "До тех пор, пока я резко не затормозила" with vpunch

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:72
translate spanish hwb_s16a_1812645c:

    # Amber "You’re kidding me."
    Amber "Да ты издеваешься."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:74
translate spanish hwb_s16a_c786b246:

    # "Marina had been slouching, but bolts upright at the sudden stop."
    "Marina estaba encorvada, pero se endereza de golpe con la parada repentina."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:78
translate spanish hwb_s16a_422e0d7c:

    # Marina "What happened?"
    Marina "Что такое?"

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:80
translate spanish hwb_s16a_2d568c92:

    # "Just a few feet ahead, in the parking lot of the diner we ate at this morning, is Mariah’s motorhome."
    "A solo unos pasos adelante, en el estacionamiento del restaurante donde desayunamos esta mañana, está la casa rodante de Mariah."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:82
translate spanish hwb_s16a_73aaa11d:

    # Amber "Look at that. It’s them."
    Amber "Смотри. Это они."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:86
translate spanish hwb_s16a_88cf4c49:

    # "I point, and Marina leans forward. When she recognizes their RV, she grins."
    "Señalo, y Marina se inclina hacia adelante. Cuando reconoce su RV, sonríe."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:88
translate spanish hwb_s16a_c0de2507:

    # Marina "Should we go see them?"
    Marina "Может нам стоит пойти встретиться с ними?"

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:92
translate spanish hwb_s16a_b122dbe9:

    # Amber "What? No way! That’s extra reason to avoid that place."
    Amber "Чего? Ни за что! Они — еще одна причина не заезжать в это место."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:98
translate spanish hwb_s16a_4a784ca7:

    # Marina "Aw, but Amber. Maybe we could see about teaming up for the treasure here or something."
    Marina "Ох, ну Эмбер. Может, мы обсудим с ними сотрудничество в поисках сокровища?"

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:100
translate spanish hwb_s16a_a0469e27:

    # Amber "That’d never happen. Mariah would rather lose every time than have our help."
    Amber "Этого никогда не случится. Мария скорее уступит нам, чем согласится на нашу помощь."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:104
translate spanish hwb_s16a_34357571:

    # Amber "Besides, it’s not like-"
    Amber "Кроме того, не похоже, что-"

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:108
translate spanish hwb_s16a_a411f26f:

    # Marina "{cps=10}Pleeeeease?{/cps}"
    Marina "{cps=10}Ну пожаааааааалуйста?{/cps}"

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:112
translate spanish hwb_s16a_92ea82d6:

    # "Already giving up in my head, I give Marina one last desperate look."
    "Ya rindiéndome en mi mente, le lanzo a Marina una última mirada desesperada."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:114
translate spanish hwb_s16a_2a96aea1:

    # Amber "Seriously?"
    Amber "Серьезно?"

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:118
translate spanish hwb_s16a_dfbf09cd:

    # Marina "Yeah! Even if we don’t team up, it’d be nice to see them again."
    Marina "Да! Даже если мы не станем командой, будет здорово увидеть их снова."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:122
translate spanish hwb_s16a_80e53927:

    # Amber "Not sure if 'nice' is the word I’d use…"
    Amber "Не уверена, что “здорово” - это подходящее слово…"

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:124
translate spanish hwb_s16a_68abac37:

    # "Despite my muttering, I flick on my blinker and change lanes, pulling into the parking lot yet again."
    "A pesar de mi murmullo, enciendo la direccional y cambio de carril, entrando al estacionamiento una vez más."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:163
translate spanish hwb_s16a_ce73f1fb:

    # "Like this morning, it seems pretty busy. I have to park next to Mariah’s RV because it’s the only open spot large enough."
    "Como esta mañana, parece estar bastante lleno. Tengo que estacionarme junto a la RV de Mariah porque es el único lugar abierto lo suficientemente grande."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:165
translate spanish hwb_s16a_8343bf1e:

    # "Marina skips out and towards the entrance while I trudge behind her."
    "Marina sale saltando hacia la entrada mientras yo arrastro los pies detrás de ella."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:169
translate spanish hwb_s16a_fadc0054:

    # "It doesn’t take long to find the Trio. Even amongst all the eccentric people that the hunt has drawn, their questionable fashion sense stands out."
    "No tarda mucho en encontrar al Trío. Incluso entre toda la gente excéntrica que ha atraído la búsqueda, su dudoso sentido de la moda destaca."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:171
translate spanish hwb_s16a_0834d514:

    # "They have a large table near the back; bigger than the one Marina and I ate at this morning. Joseph and Tess share a bench, while Mariah’s spread across the opposite side."
    "Tienen una mesa grande cerca del fondo; más grande que la que Marina y yo ocupamos esta mañana. Joseph y Tess comparten un banco, mientras que Mariah está extendida en el lado opuesto."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:173
translate spanish hwb_s16a_80cd7d1f:

    # "It’s probably supposed to look sultry, but it comes across more like the bench is devouring her."
    "Probablemente se supone que debe verse sensual, pero más bien parece que el banco la está devorando."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:175
translate spanish hwb_s16a_c3f0503f:

    # "When she sees them, Marina scurries to the back, hand raised in greeting. I bring up the rear, still slow."
    "Cuando los ve, Marina corre hacia el fondo, con la mano levantada en señal de saludo. Yo voy detrás, todavía lenta."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:205
translate spanish hwb_s16a_06ee627a:

    # Marina "Hey guys!"
    Marina "Привет, ребят!"

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:207
translate spanish hwb_s16a_d6c0be32:

    # "Tess and Joseph both wave, the latter smiling when he sees us. Mariah looks surprised for a second, but then scowls and turns towards the wall."
    "Tess y Joseph saludan con la mano, este último sonriendo al vernos. Mariah se ve sorprendida por un segundo, pero luego frunce el ceño y se vuelve hacia la pared."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:209
translate spanish hwb_s16a_df7fbc97:

    # "The feeling is mutual."
    "El sentimiento es mutuo."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:211
translate spanish hwb_s16a_78559a7c:

    # Joseph "Hey, imagine running into you two here. Just get into town?"
    Joseph "Эй, классно напороться на вас тут. Вы только приехали?"

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:213
translate spanish hwb_s16a_bcade808:

    # Marina "Nope, we’ve been here all day."
    Marina "Неа, мы тут уже весь день."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:215
translate spanish hwb_s16a_4b081bd7:

    # Marina "We actually ate breakfast at this place this morning!"
    Marina "Мы даже успели позавтракать в этой закусочной!"

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:220
translate spanish hwb_s16a_3eefbd76:

    # Amber "Yeah, you’re always a couple steps behind us, I guess."
    Amber "Ага, похоже, вы всегда на пару шагов позади нас."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:225
translate spanish hwb_s16a_ebebcaf7:

    # "Mariah’s glare is stonier than Double Arch itself. But of course she keeps looking at the wall, instead of us."
    "La mirada de Mariah es más dura que el propio Double Arch. Pero, por supuesto, sigue mirando a la pared, en lugar de a nosotras."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:229
translate spanish hwb_s16a_e87ee485:

    # "Joseph laughs, though."
    "Joseph se ríe, sin embargo."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:231
translate spanish hwb_s16a_5a1753e6:

    # Joseph "Here, let's break bread."
    Joseph "Вот, давайте разделим трапезу вместе."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:233
translate spanish hwb_s16a_2c5be46a:

    # "He and Tess scoot down the booth, making some room which Marina promptly fills."
    "Él y Tess se deslizan en el asiento, haciendo un espacio que Marina ocupa de inmediato."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:237
translate spanish hwb_s16a_1b5332a1:

    # "I’m left next to the smoldering fury that is Mariah."
    "Me quedo junto a la furia humeante que es Mariah."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:239
translate spanish hwb_s16a_6e83605d:

    # "She moves her leg, just a little, but enough for me to sit down."
    "Ella mueve la pierna, solo un poco, pero lo suficiente para que yo me siente."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:243
translate spanish hwb_s16a_71f0f491:

    # Amber "Thanks. Sorry to barge in on you guys like this."
    Amber "Спасибо. Простите, что потеснили вас."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:245
translate spanish hwb_s16a_d1cf6b6b:

    # Joseph "Ah, it’s no problem. More the merrier."
    Joseph "Ах, не проблема. Чем больше, тем веселее."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:249
translate spanish hwb_s16a_2edc37b5:

    # Mariah "I hope you don’t expect us to cover your bill."
    Mariah "Надеюсь, вы не ждете, что мы будем платить за вас."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:251
translate spanish hwb_s16a_2b420615:

    # "Groaning, Joe pats his hands over Tess' ears."
    "Gimiendo, Joe pone las manos sobre las orejas de Tess."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:256
translate spanish hwb_s16a_896bb1f9:

    # Joseph "Could you at least {i}try{/i} not to be a pain in the ass between the hours of 5pm and 6 in the morning? It would make my life a lot easier."
    Joseph "Может ты {i}попытаешься{/i} не быть занозой в заднице, хотя бы в промежуток между 5-ю вечера и 6-ю часами утра? Это бы серьезно облегчило мою жизнь и я был бы тааак счастлив."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:258
translate spanish hwb_s16a_447e2ca9:

    # "He uncovers Tess' ears and gives us a blank look."
    "Descubre las orejas de Tess y nos mira sin expresión."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:262
translate spanish hwb_s16a_357c8414:

    # Joseph "She's right, though. There's no way we can afford that."
    Joseph "Но она права. Мы просто не можем себе этого позволить."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:267
translate spanish hwb_s16a_409da303:

    # Tess "We had to dine and dash for breakfast."
    Tess "Мы поели и сбежали, не заплатив за завтрак."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:273
translate spanish hwb_s16a_ea5a883a:

    # Amber "Uhhh... So what about you? How long have you been here?"
    Amber "Эммм... Так что на счет вас? Как давно вы тут?"

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:277
translate spanish hwb_s16a_bbd8aab7:

    # Joseph "We got in around lunchtime. Spent forever and a half stuck in traffic though."
    Joseph "Мы приехали где-то около обеда. Но потратили целую вечность, пока стояли в пробках."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:279
translate spanish hwb_s16a_235b0d4c:

    # "He sounds worn out. I wonder if Mariah ever lets him drive. Or makes him."
    "Suena agotado. Me pregunto si Mariah alguna vez lo deja conducir. O lo obliga."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:283
translate spanish hwb_s16a_6070db1c:

    # Amber "Us too. We were gonna look around Double Arch but it was too busy."
    Amber "Мы тоже. Мы собирались поискать рядом с “Двойной” аркой, но там было слишком многолюдно."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:285
translate spanish hwb_s16a_431c544f:

    # Joseph "Yeah, we took one look at it and just kept driving. Didn’t even wanna try."
    Joseph "Ага, мы взглянули на нее и проехали мимо, даже не хотелось пытаться в таких условиях."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:289
translate spanish hwb_s16a_32080127:

    # Tess "Sis said that anyone who bothered to get out was a fu-"
    Tess "Сестренка сказала, что те, кто пытался туда добраться - ебл-"

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:295
translate spanish hwb_s16a_6c8dc080:

    # Mariah "You weren’t supposed to hear that!"
    Mariah "Ты не должна была этого слышать!"

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:299
translate spanish hwb_s16a_df0b4e92:

    # Joseph "I told you, this girl hears everything."
    Joseph "Я тебя предупреждал. Она слышит все."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:306
translate spanish hwb_s16a_a38fe680:

    # Joseph "Anyway, we were thinking about heading back this evening; see if it maybe it’s cleared out some."
    Joseph "Так или иначе, мы подумали вернуться туда вечером, вдруг там уже будет поменьше народу."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:311
translate spanish hwb_s16a_989f7f7d:

    # Marina "We were gonna do that too! I was telling Amber that we should see if maybe you guys wanted to team up and we could look together."
    Marina "Мы тоже собирались так сделать! А еще я сказала Эмбер, что может быть вы, ребята, захотите объединиться в команду."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:317
translate spanish hwb_s16a_a5aaeac1:

    # "{color=#ee320f}Amber{/color} & {color=#ffdab3}Mariah{/color}" "Hell no!" with hpunch
    MariahAmber "Ни за что!" with hpunch

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:327
translate spanish hwb_s16a_8d8ebf8e:

    # "The two of us look at each other. Seems all that we ever agree on is not sticking together."
    "Nos miramos la una a la otra. Parece que lo único en lo que coincidimos es en no mantenernos unidas."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:333
translate spanish hwb_s16a_4e9bdba3:

    # Amber "Uh, no offense to you, Joe."
    Amber "Эх, без обид, Джо."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:337
translate spanish hwb_s16a_78238e4f:

    # Amber "Just didn’t wanna… You know…"
    Amber "Я просто не хочу… Ну ты понимаешь…"

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:339
translate spanish hwb_s16a_9f9effc9:

    # "I trail off, trying to think of an excuse that isn’t 'didn’t wanna deal with Mariah.' Which is the truth."
    "Me quedo en blanco, tratando de pensar en una excusa que no sea \"no quería lidiar con Mariah\". Que es la verdad."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:341
translate spanish hwb_s16a_f7b0008f:

    # "But Joseph just laughs and waves it off."
    "Pero Joseph solo se ríe y lo ignora."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:345
translate spanish hwb_s16a_89c535b7:

    # Joseph "Nah, I get what you mean. Don’t think Mariah would be too fond of splitting the goods either."
    Joseph "Мэх, я понял, что ты имеешь в виду. Не думаю, что Мария тоже будет готова поделиться найденным."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:350
translate spanish hwb_s16a_5e7a1729:

    # "Marina frowns, but perks back up after just a second."
    "Marina frunce el ceño, pero se anima de nuevo al instante."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:354
translate spanish hwb_s16a_26c7e8bc:

    # "Soon, a waitress comes to take our order. Marina and I are careful to order meals on the smaller side: just sandwiches with fries."
    "Pronto, una mesera viene a tomar nuestra orden. Marina y yo tenemos cuidado de pedir comidas pequeñas: solo sándwiches con papas fritas."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:356
translate spanish hwb_s16a_bb58d3f7:

    # "On the other hand, Mariah’s order comes with a bunch of requirements as to what can and can’t be on it."
    "Por otro lado, la orden de Mariah viene con un montón de requisitos sobre qué puede y no puede llevar."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:358
translate spanish hwb_s16a_4bdbff07:

    # "By the time she’s made so many substitutions and extras, it hardly resembles the item described in the menu."
    "Para cuando ha hecho tantas sustituciones y extras, apenas se parece al artículo descrito en el menú."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:362
translate spanish hwb_s16a_d3a6eff4:

    # Joseph "So, I can tell you ladies that it’s not at the Parade of Elephants, and Delicate Arch was a no-go too. Think we might try Skyline next."
    Joseph "Ну, дамы, хочу вам сказать, что сокровище не под “Парадом слонов” и точно не под “Ажурной аркой”, думаю, дальше мы попробуем поискать под аркой “Скайлайн”."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:366
translate spanish hwb_s16a_8b51f5bf:

    # Amber "Good luck, I guess. Wonder how many of those the miner would’ve known about though. Pretty sure this park wasn’t founded 'til after the Gold Rush."
    Amber "Удачи с этим. Интересно, сколько из них были известны этому старателю. Уверена, что те, которые ты назвал еще не были открыты во времена золотой лихорадки."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:368
translate spanish hwb_s16a_7e6d9695:

    # "Joseph shrugs."
    "Joseph se encoge de hombros."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:372
translate spanish hwb_s16a_8bad432c:

    # Marina "Amber knows a lot about these places! She’s like an encyclopedia."
    Marina "Эмбер знает столько всего про это место! Она как ходячая энциклопедия."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:374
translate spanish hwb_s16a_4d2ec552:

    # "I can feel my face flush like always when she praises me."
    "Siento que mi cara se sonroja, como siempre que ella me elogia."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:381
translate spanish hwb_s16a_5faff8f8:

    # Amber "Not really. I just know bits and pieces."
    Amber "Не совсем. Я знаю какими-то отрывками."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:385
translate spanish hwb_s16a_deaf930d:

    # Joseph "Still something to be proud of. Aren't too many girls your age who care about anything that happened more than five years ago."
    Joseph "Но все же есть чем гордиться. Не так много девушек твоего возраста интересуются чем-то, что произошло более пяти лет назад."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:389
translate spanish hwb_s16a_406a61bd:

    # Amber "It’s really nothing special. I just spent a lot of time on the road when I was younger."
    Amber "Ну правда, ничего особенного в этом нет. Просто я провела достаточно много времени путешествуя когда была младше."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:393
translate spanish hwb_s16a_f20ab43a:

    # Joseph "That so?"
    Joseph "Правда?"

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:397
translate spanish hwb_s16a_3917d85e:

    # "I appreciate his leaving it as an open-ended question, rather than prying. Marina looks at me, eyes wide, probably to see if I’m about to cry or something."
    "Agradezco que deje la pregunta abierta, en lugar de indagar. Marina me mira, con los ojos muy abiertos, probablemente para ver si voy a llorar o algo."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:403
translate spanish hwb_s16a_131932e3:

    # "I try to be nonchalant."
    "Intento mostrarme despreocupada."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:407
translate spanish hwb_s16a_6a7b434b:

    # Amber "Yeah, until I was in middle school. My grandpa used to drive me all over the country."
    Amber "Ага, пока я была в младшей школе, мы с дедушкой путешествовали по всей стране."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:411
translate spanish hwb_s16a_fedccc0b:

    # Joseph "Sounds like a fun time."
    Joseph "Звучит здоровски."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:413
translate spanish hwb_s16a_a112fd78:

    # Amber "It was."
    Amber "Так и было."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:415
translate spanish hwb_s16a_fb888e17:

    # Amber "He uh…"
    Amber "Он…"

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:417
translate spanish hwb_s16a_a5361de6:

    # "Guess there’s no point in hiding it. Plus, Joseph has this kind of disarming air to him. Like he exudes calmness."
    "Supongo que no tiene caso ocultarlo. Además, Joseph tiene ese aire desarmante. Como si irradiara calma."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:421
translate spanish hwb_s16a_6260559a:

    # Amber "Passed away a little while ago. Still a little…"
    Amber "Покинул меня недавно. Совсем недавно…"

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:423
translate spanish hwb_s16a_b7dde4eb:

    # "I tap my throat, hoping that gets my point across."
    "Me toco la garganta, esperando que eso deje claro mi punto."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:425
translate spanish hwb_s16a_3c5ee22e:

    # "It does. Joseph nods."
    "Lo hace. Joseph asiente."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:429
translate spanish hwb_s16a_fa697b25:

    # Joseph "I’m sorry for your loss."
    Joseph "Я скорблю о твоей утрате."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:433
translate spanish hwb_s16a_1131e1bc:

    # Amber "Thanks."
    Amber "Спасибо."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:437
translate spanish hwb_s16a_1e0ad1b0:

    # "Marina’s eyes flick between me and Joseph. She must be pretty worried. So I force a smile, even though I can feel that growing glumness that shows up anytime I talk about Gramps."
    "La mirada de Marina va de mí a Joseph. Debe estar muy preocupada. Así que fuerzo una sonrisa, aunque siento esa creciente melancolía que aparece cada vez que hablo del Abuelo."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:443
translate spanish hwb_s16a_9eb43dd4:

    # Amber "Meeting this dork has helped a lot, though."
    Amber "Однако встреча с этой занудой мне очень помогла."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:445
translate spanish hwb_s16a_73b9d361:

    # "I jerk my chin towards Marina, who looks shocked. As if I could’ve been talking about anyone else."
    "Señalo con la barbilla hacia Marina, quien se ve impactada. Como si pudiera haber estado hablando de otra persona."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:447
translate spanish hwb_s16a_d511dbf0:

    # Amber "Spent a while moping around before that."
    Amber "До того я тратила много времени на депрессию."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:451
translate spanish hwb_s16a_06f9fb4c:

    # Tess "Family is good."
    Tess "Семья это здорово."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:455
translate spanish hwb_s16a_f584912f:

    # "I blink. It’s so easy to forget she’s there."
    "Parpadeo. Es tan fácil olvidar que ella está ahí."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:457
translate spanish hwb_s16a_25aa6464:

    # Amber "Yeah, definitely."
    Amber "Ага, точно."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:459
translate spanish hwb_s16a_8173321d:

    # "I hadn’t really thought of it before, but Tess seems to be in a similar situation I was. Growing up on the go and all."
    "No lo había pensado antes, pero Tess parece estar en una situación similar a la mía. Creciendo siempre en movimiento y todo eso."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:461
translate spanish hwb_s16a_8740231d:

    # "I’m curious how it happened, but I won’t ask. Not my place."
    "Me da curiosidad cómo sucedió, pero no preguntaré. No es mi lugar."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:469
translate spanish hwb_s16a_fa8d8f0d:

    # Mariah "So what are you going to do?"
    Mariah "Так что вы будете делать?"

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:473
translate spanish hwb_s16a_1220824c:

    # Amber "Huh?"
    Amber "Хм?"

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:477
translate spanish hwb_s16a_34228a0a:

    # Mariah "When all this is over."
    Mariah "Когда все это кончится."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:479
translate spanish hwb_s16a_32e2e55e:

    # "She gestures around."
    "Ella señala alrededor."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:483
translate spanish hwb_s16a_a17de36c:

    # Amber "Dinner?"
    Amber "Когда кончится обед?"

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:487
translate spanish hwb_s16a_82c04e82:

    # Mariah "No, dumbass! I meant the treasure hunt."
    Mariah "Нет, тупица! Охота за сокровищами."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:491
translate spanish hwb_s16a_9dd29a83:

    # Mariah "Forget it. I don’t actually care."
    Mariah "Хотя забудь, мне все равно."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:495
translate spanish hwb_s16a_94953abf:

    # Amber "Dunno yet. Mare and I have been kind of talking about that."
    Amber "Хрен знает. Мы с Мари как раз размышляли об этом."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:500
translate spanish hwb_s16a_8c2f1939:

    # Marina "Apparently she wants to become a financial advisor."
    Marina "Похоже, что она хочет сдать финансовым консультантом."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:504
translate spanish hwb_s16a_78bfc87f:

    # Amber "Actually, financial advisors are a poor source of long-term growth, as actively managed funds tend to be outperformed by index funds and lose a large share of their gains due to excessive management fees."
    Amber "На самом деле, финансовый брокер - весьма посредственный источник доходов, так как они очень сильно зависят от фондовых индексов и частенько теряют значительные средства из-за поборов, налогов и рыночных факторов."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:508
translate spanish hwb_s16a_7dcc4288:

    # Marina "Oh my God Amber, nobody cares."
    Marina "Господи, Эмбер, всем вообще наплевать."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:512
translate spanish hwb_s16a_f7e374b2:

    # Amber "I'll be caring all the way to my maxed out Roth IRA."
    Amber "Я буду всячески стремиться к заключению персонального пенсионного соглашения, чтобы выжать максимум."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:516
translate spanish hwb_s16a_a0daa2ff:

    # Marina "She’s gonna buy three mansions."
    Marina "Она купит несколько особняков."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:520
translate spanish hwb_s16a_6293e891:

    # Amber "Yeah, that. I’ll have plenty of time to figure stuff out in my mansions."
    Amber "Ага, как она и сказала. И у меня будет куча времени обдумать все мысли в моих владениях."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:522
translate spanish hwb_s16a_df8335ed:

    # "Three of us chuckle, but then the conversation trails off. Tess and Marina are working on coloring Tess's menu. From what I can see, it has different characters than the one this morning."
    "Los tres reímos, pero luego la conversación se desvanece. Tess y Marina están coloreando el menú de Tess. Por lo que veo, tiene personajes diferentes al de esta mañana."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:524
translate spanish hwb_s16a_7f9d9084:

    # "They look like they make a good team. Each of them work on separate pictures, but switch from time to time."
    "Parece que hacen un buen equipo. Cada una trabaja en dibujos separados, pero se turnan de vez en cuando."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:528
translate spanish hwb_s16a_fa3080f9:

    # "So Marina will color the hair on one character, then Tess colors the clothes. Despite not talking at all, they don’t ever get in each other’s way."
    "Así que Marina colorea el cabello de un personaje, luego Tess colorea la ropa. A pesar de no hablar en absoluto, nunca se estorban."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:532
translate spanish hwb_s16a_1c93a65e:

    # "Joseph also observes from above, smiling slightly. He’s usually the one to play with Tess, so it must be nice for her to have some company."
    "Joseph también observa desde arriba, sonriendo ligeramente. Él suele jugar con Tess, así que debe ser agradable para ella tener compañía."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:536
translate spanish hwb_s16a_36fa1953:

    # "On the other hand, like a jug of milk, Mariah’s mood seems to be getting more and more sour."
    "Por otro lado, como una jarra de leche, el humor de Mariah parece volverse cada vez más agrio."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:538
translate spanish hwb_s16a_4e34551b:

    # "I don’t even know what she’s mad about this time. Maybe something happened before we showed up. Or maybe it’s because we showed up."
    "Ni siquiera sé por qué está enojada esta vez. Quizás pasó algo antes de que llegáramos. O tal vez es porque llegamos."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:540
translate spanish hwb_s16a_2d8e48a5:

    # "Either way, she ought to have memorized every single detail of the wall she’s been staring at this entire time."
    "De cualquier forma, ya debería haberse memorizado cada detalle de la pared que ha estado mirando todo este tiempo."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:542
translate spanish hwb_s16a_0c063e72:

    # "She doesn’t look up until our food arrives a little bit later."
    "No levanta la vista hasta que nuestra comida llega un poco después."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:546
translate spanish hwb_s16a_75367717:

    # "It’s a good thing we have a large table, because there’s still hardly any room left once all the plates are set down."
    "Menos mal que tenemos una mesa grande, porque apenas queda espacio una vez que colocan todos los platos."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:548
translate spanish hwb_s16a_585af700:

    # "My sandwich is so big, it takes two hands to hold. And I have enough fries to sustain Ireland for the winter."
    "Mi sándwich es tan grande que necesito ambas manos para sostenerlo. Y tengo suficientes papas fritas para alimentar a Irlanda durante el invierno."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:552
translate spanish hwb_s16a_96a8c7f0:

    # "When Marina picks up her sandwich, all the ingredients pour out the back. She quickly gives up trying to reconstruct it and just uses a knife and fork instead."
    "Cuando Marina toma su sándwich, todos los ingredientes se derraman por detrás. Rápidamente se rinde al intentar reconstruirlo y usa cuchillo y tenedor en su lugar."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:554
translate spanish hwb_s16a_a3fed042:

    # "Watching the other three eat is amusing, too. Joseph chews with slow, measured bites whereas Mariah attacks her meal like it owes her money."
    "Ver a los otros tres comer también es divertido. Joseph mastica con bocados lentos y medidos, mientras que Mariah ataca su comida como si le debiera dinero."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:558
translate spanish hwb_s16a_275dcbc0:

    # "Across from her, Tess is cutting up chicken tenders with surgical precision."
    "Al otro lado de ella, Tess corta sus tiras de pollo con precisión quirúrgica."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:562
translate spanish hwb_s16a_034ba62c:

    # "Marina catches me staring and smiles at me covertly. Seems she noticed too."
    "Marina me atrapa mirando y me sonríe a escondidas. Parece que ella también lo notó."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:564
translate spanish hwb_s16a_228c4ea1:

    # "Mariah's the first to finish eating."
    "Mariah es la primera en terminar de comer."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:566
translate spanish hwb_s16a_2f339a4a:

    # "I'm just a couple bites behind. That's embarrassing."
    "Solo me faltan un par de bocados. Qué vergüenza."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:568
translate spanish hwb_s16a_6dbfc5ad:

    # "She wipes her face with a napkin then finally looks at me."
    "Se limpia la cara con una servilleta y finalmente me mira."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:572
translate spanish hwb_s16a_72b8a4f0:

    # Mariah "Where are you two staying?"
    Mariah "А где вы двое решили остановиться?"

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:574
translate spanish hwb_s16a_1503d53c:

    # "It could be an innocent question, or it could be a trap."
    "Podría ser una pregunta inocente, o podría ser una trampa."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:578
translate spanish hwb_s16a_0e9cd519:

    # Amber "Around. We’ll find a parking lot somewhere."
    Amber "Где-нибудь. Найдем какую-то парковку поблизости."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:582
translate spanish hwb_s16a_25ce6927:

    # Mariah "You thieves are gonna have a late start, then."
    Mariah "Значит вы, воры, начнете позже..."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:584
translate spanish hwb_s16a_8ccb3a49:

    # Amber "I guess. Don’t tell me you planned ahead and got a campsite."
    Amber "Может быть. Даже не говори мне, что ты все распланировала и уже заготовила место для ночлега."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:588
translate spanish hwb_s16a_c0039560:

    # Mariah "Don't be stupid. Of course not."
    Mariah "Не тупи. Конечно же нет."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:593
translate spanish hwb_s16a_e99c7e9c:

    # Mariah "Wait, that’s not what I meant."
    Mariah "Хотя стой, это не то, что я имела в виду,"

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:595
translate spanish hwb_s16a_b59f9738:

    # "I scoff as she backtracks to keep from insulting herself."
    "Me río mientras ella se retracta para no insultarse a sí misma."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:599
translate spanish hwb_s16a_b759c05f:

    # Mariah "What I mean is, there’s no way they’re gonna bother checking every single permit. There’s too much going on right now."
    Mariah "Я имела в виду, что они не будут следить за всеми правилами и указаниями, слишком уж много всего тут происходит."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:601
translate spanish hwb_s16a_4ede3724:

    # Mariah "Just pick a nice spot out of the way, don’t make trouble, and it’ll be fine."
    Mariah "Так что можно просто выбрать себе симпатичное место для стоянки, чтобы никому не причинять неудобство и все - все будет отлично."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:603
translate spanish hwb_s16a_97e60c21:

    # "Joe flatly stares at Mariah."
    "Joe mira fijamente a Mariah."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:605
translate spanish hwb_s16a_3362af6b:

    # Joseph "Easier said than done."
    Joseph "Проще сказать, чем сделать."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:607
translate spanish hwb_s16a_0bfc67eb:

    # Amber "Good luck with that. I don’t wanna take the risk."
    Amber "Ну, удачи с этим, я не готова так рисковать."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:609
translate spanish hwb_s16a_087c6afc:

    # "On foot, if you’re trespassing and get caught, most of the time you’ll just get thrown out."
    "A pie, si estás invadiendo propiedad y te atrapan, la mayoría de las veces solo te echarán."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:611
translate spanish hwb_s16a_ffd9cd42:

    # "But I don’t want our license plate getting written down or something if we were to do what she suggests."
    "Pero no quiero que nos anoten la placa o algo así si hiciéramos lo que ella sugiere."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:613
translate spanish hwb_s16a_f2512be3:

    # "Mariah shrugs."
    "Mariah se encoge de hombros."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:617
translate spanish hwb_s16a_15db20aa:

    # Mariah "Suit yourself. Don’t say I didn’t never try to help you."
    Mariah "Располагайся как удобнее. И не говори, что я не разу ни пыталась тебе помочь."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:621
translate spanish hwb_s16a_1dd3d8c4:

    # Tess "Didn’t ever."
    Tess "“Ни разу не пыталась”."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:625
translate spanish hwb_s16a_5d3b7736:

    # Joseph "You ever camp here before, Amber? Sounded like you know the place."
    Joseph "Ты здесь раньше останавливать, Эмбер? Похоже, ты бывала тут."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:627
translate spanish hwb_s16a_1b9481ea:

    # Amber "Long time ago. I don’t remember a whole lot. Just good at remembering names, I guess."
    Amber "Давным-давно. Я не особо что-то помню. Наверное, я хороша только в запоминании названий и имен."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:631
translate spanish hwb_s16a_b282a9f9:

    # Joseph "Useful skill to have."
    Joseph "Но это полезный навык."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:633
translate spanish hwb_s16a_d5d7e533:

    # Amber "Yeah. Used to be, before we’d go anywhere, Gramps and I would research the place we were going. History and stuff like that."
    Amber "Ага. Раньше, перед тем, как поехать куда-то, мы с дедушкой подолгу изучали эти места, их историю и все в таком роде."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:635
translate spanish hwb_s16a_18509e94:

    # Joseph "You sure learned a lot of useful stuff from him, huh?"
    Joseph "Ты многому научилась от него, да?"

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:637
translate spanish hwb_s16a_a094de3a:

    # Amber "Yep, always wanted to make him proud. He used to say I was a real chip off the…"
    Amber "Да. Всегда хотела заставить его гордиться собой. Он всегда говорил, что я была его маленькой копи…"

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:646
translate spanish hwb_s16a_755d4c10:

    # "My words catch in my throat. Not because I’m emotional, but because I just realized something. Remembered it, rather."
    "Las palabras se me atoran en la garganta. No porque esté emocionada, sino porque acabo de darme cuenta de algo. Recordarlo, más bien."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:652
translate spanish hwb_s16a_7cfd54ab:

    # "Mariah and Joe know it too. Mine and Mariah's eyes lock, and she bolts up at my words. The other two look confused."
    "Mariah y Joe también lo saben. Mis ojos y los de Mariah se encuentran, y ella se levanta de golpe al oír mis palabras. Los otros dos se ven confundidos."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:658
translate spanish hwb_s16a_f5fb3054:

    # "{color=#ee320f}Amber{/color} & {color=#ffdab3}Mariah{/color}" "We’re leaving!"
    MariahAmber "Мы уходим!"

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:683
translate spanish hwb_s16a_de175459:

    # "Mariah sprints for the door without paying and I nearly yank Marina’s arm out of its socket as we run to the exit. Other diners turn to watch us, but I barely notice them."
    "Mariah sale corriendo hacia la puerta sin pagar, y casi le arranco el brazo a Marina de su cuenca mientras corremos hacia la salida. Otros comensales se giran a mirarnos, pero apenas los noto."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:687
translate spanish hwb_s16a_e39b5d10:

    # Marina "Amber! What the heck?"
    Marina "Эмбер! Какого черта?"

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:689
translate spanish hwb_s16a_f91170fe:

    # "Her voice is shaky from being jolted around."
    "Su voz tiembla por los sacudones."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:691
translate spanish hwb_s16a_a7d5d4ab:

    # Amber "I know where the treasure is."
    Amber "Я знаю, где сокровища."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:693
translate spanish hwb_s16a_85e30448:

    # "I yell behind me as I turn to look, and see the Trio exit the restaurant close behind us. Joe’s carrying Tess on his back."
    "Grito por detrás mientras me giro a mirar, y veo al Trío salir del restaurante justo detrás de nosotros. Joe lleva a Tess en su espalda."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:695
translate spanish hwb_s16a_056b7d5f:

    # Amber "I know where it is."
    Amber "Я знаю где оно."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:697
translate spanish hwb_s16a_0398d1e3:

    # "I say it again to assure myself."
    "Lo repito para asegurarme a mí misma."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:699
translate spanish hwb_s16a_e6a427bc:

    # "We reach the motorhome seconds after Mariah and her crew reach theirs. I practically hurl Marina up and into her spot before I leap into my own."
    "Llegamos a la casa rodante segundos después de que Mariah y su equipo lleguen a la suya. Prácticamente lanzo a Marina hacia arriba y a su asiento antes de saltar al mío."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:701
translate spanish hwb_s16a_9cc8a80d:

    # "Not even bothering to buckle up, I hurry towards the road."
    "Sin siquiera molestarme en abrocharme el cinturón, acelero hacia la carretera."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:251
translate spanish hwb_s16a_89a6ff7a:

    # "Groaning, Joe puts his hands over Tess' ears."
    "Gimiendo, Joe se tapa los oídos de Tess con las manos."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:429
translate spanish hwb_s16a_b490516a:

    # Joseph "I’m sorry for your loss. I know how hard that can be..."
    Joseph "Я скорблю о твоей утрате."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:463 Google Translate starts here, since these are brand new lines
translate spanish hwb_s16a_d48cf75f:

    # "A far-off look seeps onto Joe's face. He stares out the window, like he's gazing at something one hundred yards away."
    "На лице Джо просачивается далекий взгляд. Он смотрит в окно, как будто он смотрит на что-то в сотне ярдов."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:465
translate spanish hwb_s16a_df8406b0:

    # "Mariah glances up at him. For a split second — if that — she even looks a little concerned. But then it's right back to business as usual."
    "Mariah levanta la mirada hacia él. Por una fracción de segundo —si acaso— hasta parece un poco preocupada. Pero luego vuelve directo a los negocios como siempre."

# game/script/hwb_s16a.rpy:467
translate spanish hwb_s16a_fdaef623:

    # "She leers over at me and shoves herself back into the conversation."
    "Me mira de reojo y se mete de nuevo en la conversación."

translate spanish strings:

    # script/hwb_s16a.rpy:72
    old "Driving through Moab"
    new "Driving through Moab"

    # script/hwb_s16a.rpy:601
    old "Waiting on food"
    new "Waiting on food"

